2. siem wazuh .... used to protect networks, virtulized environments and cloud environments, SIEM security information Event management, Wazuh is used to collect, aggregate, index and analyze security data, helping organizations detect intrusions, threats and behavioral anomalies. As cyber threats are becoming more sophisticated, real-time monitoring and security analysis are needed for fast threat detection and remediation.
Wazuh features:
i. security analytics
ii. intitution detection
iii. cloud security 
iv. vunerability detections
